      "id": "PopularPost5464",
      "post_content": "Oh boy... one of those \"love it or hate it\" cards... At First glance it looks better than it is, but it's still not bad...  \n  \nA 3/3 flyer for 5.. meh.. could do better. Pay three and all your creatures gain shroud... only so/so.  \nI would rather the card said \"UG: Target creature you control gains shroud\"  \n  \nCost wise, its another one of those that is hard to judge, it looks to be priced exactly right, which would make it useless... but still...",
