      "id": "PopularPost28631",
      "post_content": "I agree with Warrior77 and Atrues. It should have Exalted, and it should target only. All creature gaining shroud is not usually very effective. It would be a good addition if it gave all of your creatures shroud until the next upkeep so tapping all mana for him isn't going to leave him and your other creatures wide open, or it had its own shroud. Nice flavor on the art, most aven are 'normal bird' like and fighters, but the [Aerie Mystics](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aerie Mystics) are smart owls that protect.",
      "posted_by": "ICEFANG13",
